headline: Royal Caribbean Group Raises Dividend Thirty Eight Percent
summary: The Board of Directors of Royal Caribbean Cruises Ltd. (NYSE: RCL) today declared a quarterly dividend of $0.55 per common share payable on January 13, 2025 to shareholders of record at the close of business on December 27, 2024. This increase reflects the company's continuing efforts to enhance shareholder returns.
